tafsir[96]{c,v,t}:
  56,1,"Si Darngal ngal darorii ko feere mun alaa."
  56,2,"Alanaa wonkii woo fennugol ngal, wano …ďe fenniraynoo ngal ka aduna."
  56,3,"Hoyfin…óinirayngal heefer…ďe bom…ďe …ďen naadeede Yiite, ngal …ďamtira fii gom…óim…ďe …ďen naadugol Aljanna."
  56,4,"Si leydi ndin dilliniroyaama dillannde mawnde."
  56,5,"Pelle …óen …óigginiroyee …óigginannde."
  56,6,"…óe wontira nden muncannde …óon, collaari sariindi ndi tabitataa."
  56,7,"Wontoyon nooneeji tati, nden √Īalnde:"
  56,8,"Ko wontiroo…ďe √Īaamo …ďen henndoray…ďe talki mun …óin ka √Īaamo. Iskin toowal e mawngu martaba ma…ď…ďe !"
  56,9,"E wontiroo…ďe nano …ďen henndoray…ďe talki mun …óin ka nano. Bone bis e …ďen yim…ďe nano !"
  56,10,"Ko adondiraynoo…ďe …ďen e golle mo∆ī∆īe ka aduna, woni ko adoytee naadeede Aljanna ka laakara."
  56,11,"Ko …ďen woni …ďadnitaa…ďe …ďen ka Allah."
  56,12,"Hi…ďe e nder Aljannaaji neeminii…ói, ka …ďe dakmitora kala noone neema."
  56,13,"Dental jeyaangal e …óee mofte, e mofte adinoo…ďe …ďen."
  56,14,"E yim…ďe see…óaa…ďe, jeyaa…ďe e mofte sakkitii…ďe …ďen, …ďen kadi ko adinoo…ďe …ďallinaa…ďe."
  56,15,"Hi…ďe e hoore dan…óe yu…ď…ďiraa…óe kaŇčŇče."
  56,16,"Hara hi…ďe so…ď…ďindii e …óen dan…óe, …ďe fewtondiri, tawa …ďe runtandirtaa."
  56,17,"Sukaa…ďe duuminaa…ďe hino wanngoo hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, ko ligganoo …ďe, …ďen nawyataa …ďe lannataa."
  56,18,"Hara hi…ďe jinndida ton e √Īeddu…óe …óe alaa uddoo…óe, e caltale uddotoo…óe, e koroy hebbiniraakoy beere ilaynde nder Aljanna nde ta∆īondirtaa."
  56,19,"Nden wa'aa wa beere aduna nden, tawde mo yarii nde o muusetaake hoore o haangataake."
  56,20,"∆Āen sukaa…ďe wanngodato hakkunde ma…ď…ďe ton kadi e muuyantee…ói …ói …ďe su…ďotoo."
  56,21,"∆Āe jinndida ton kadi e teewu colli ngu …ďe tuuyatee."
  56,22,"Hino woodani …ďe ka Aljanna ton kadi, rew…ďe labaa…ďe yoo…óa e yaaja gitee…ďe"
  56,23,"Wa'u…ďe wa kaŇčŇče lu'ulu'u reenaa…óe nder oogir…óe."
  56,24,"∆äum ko njo…ďdi golle ma…ď…ďe mo∆ī∆īe …óen aduna."
  56,25,"∆Āe nanataa ka nder Aljanna ton, haala bonuka, wanaa ko fawata jom mun bakkaat."
  56,26,"∆Āe nanataa ton si wanaa ko Malaa'ika'en sa…ónata …ďe kon, e ko …ďe salmondirta hakkonde ma…ď…ďe kon."
  56,27,"E joman en √Īaame tottirtee…ďe …óeri mum en juu…óe √Īaame, alah ko …ďuri mawnude …ďe daraja e ngonko ka Alla."
  56,28,"∆Āe wonoyay e le…ó…óe …óe alaa bulle-gi*e-, …óe lorrataa."
  56,29,"E banaanaaje suku…óe, weertiraa…óe yoga e dow yoga."
  56,30,"E …óowdi duumiindi, …ói iwataa."
  56,31,"E ndiyam juuray…óam, …óam ta∆īondirtaa."
  56,32,"E …ďi…ó…ďe le…ó…óe …óuu…óu…óe ko limotaako."
  56,33,"∆äe ta∆īondirantaa…ďe fes, …óe alaa yonta, huunde kadi toŇčataa …óe."
  56,34,"∆Āe wonay e leecee toownaa…óe e hoore dan…óe."
  56,35,"Ko Menen woni ko tagi …ďen huurul'aynii…ďe fu…ó…ói …ďe."
  56,36,"Men wa…ói …ďe curbaa…ďe …ďe yiidaali e gorko."
  56,37,"Rew…ďe yi…óu…ďe moodii…ďe mun, goree…ďe."
  56,38,"Men tagir …ďen, fii yim…ďe √Īaamo …ďen, maande maloore ma…ď…ďe nden."
  56,39,"∆Āen ko dental jeyaa…ďe e mofte Annabaa…ďe adinoo…ďe …ďen."
  56,40,"E see…óaa…ďe jeyaa…ďe e mofte Annabiijo Muhammadu …óen (yo o his) mofte sakkitii…ďe …ďen."
  56,41,"E jom en nane tottirtee…ďe …óeri mum en e nane mum en ndaw ko boni alhaaleeji e battane."
  56,42,"∆Āen no e henndu tii…óundu nguleeki, e ndiyam tii…óu…óam fatugol."
  56,43,"E …óowdi iwndi e curki …ďawluki."
  56,44,"Wanaa henndu …ďuu…ďundu, wanaa labaandu yi*annde."
  56,45,"Ado …ďe wonnde e …óee lepte ma…ď…ďe, hari ko …ďe neeminanoo…ďe aduna, …ďe alaano himme si wanaa tuuyooji ma…ď…ďe."
  56,46,"∆Āe laatino hi…ďe ha…ď…ďitoo e yeddugol Allah, rewa sanamu ko woori Mo."
  56,47,"Hari hi…ďe yeddaynoo ummital, …ďe jalkita fii maggal …ďe wi'a: Enee, hara si men maayii, men wontii mbullaari e ∆īi'e ki…ó…óe, hara men wuurnitete …ďaawo …óum?"
  56,48,"Hay baabiraa…ďe amen adinoo…ďe men kadi …ďen maayude immintinoyte?"
  56,49,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ďee fennu…ďe fii ummital : Pellet, yim…ďe adinoo…ďe e sakkitii…ďe fow e mun."
  56,50,"Ko on moo…ďoytee…ďe √Ďalnde Darngal feere mun alaa, fii √Īaaweede yo…ďitee."
  56,51,"Refti onon fennoo…ďe ummital majju…ďe laawol poocingol ko √Īaamoo…ďe √Īande darnga e …ďesnaa…óe lekki Jaqquum ko kiin …ďuri bonde e so…ďde …ďesnaa…óe."
  56,52,"56:51"
  56,53,"Leggal ngal hebbiiroyton dim…óe mun haa…óu…óe, deedi mon yeewu…ói."
  56,54,"Surkoron ngal ndiyam wul…óam haa fati."
  56,55,"On …óu…ó…óiniroyay yarugol e maggal, wano ngelooba …óu…ó…óinirta yarugol si √Īawii."
  56,56,"Ko on √Īaametee mettu…óo e ndiyam haa…óu…óo, woni ko …ďe ja…ď…ďortee √Īalnde njo…ďdi kuu…óe mon."
  56,57,"Ko Menen tagi on, onon yo fennu…ďe ummital, hari on woodaaka. Ko ha…ói on goonginnde wonnde Men wuurnitay on si on maayii?"
  56,58,"Onon …ďee yim…ďe, on yi'ii maniiyu mo rufoton on e rennga rew…ďe …ďen?"
  56,59,"Ko onon tagata on maniiyu? Kaa ko Menen woni tagoo…ďe mo?"
  56,60,"Ko Menen woni ko hoddiri maayde nden hakkunde mon; gooto kala e lajal, aditotaako wattintaako. Men wonaali ronkitee…ďe."
  56,61,"E wattitugol honoo…ďe mon e tagudu e mbaadi mon, Men fu…ó…óira on e ko on anndaano e tagudu e mbaadi."
  56,62,"Gom…óii hi…óon anndi no Men tagiri on non ka aranun. E on taskotaako anndon wonnde tagu…óo On aranun …óum, hino hattani immintingol on si on maayii?"
  56,63,"On yi'ii gabbe …óe sankoton …óen ka leydi?"
  56,64,"Ko onon fu…óinta …óen gabbe? Kaa ko Menen?"
  56,65,"Si Men haajuno wa…óugol ndun remuru foron, ko pellet, Men wattayno mo …óum, fewndo ka …ďadini ∆īo∆īugol. Wattinon …ďaawo …óum, hi…óon Ňčal…óa e ko he…ďu ngu."
  56,66,"Wi'on : Menen ko men leptiraa…ďe hayrugol ko men nafqi kon."
  56,67,"Wurin ko men haaa…ďe arsike."
  56,68,"On yi'ii ndiyam …óam yaroton …óam si on …óom…óaama?"
  56,69,"E ko onon saa∆īiniri …óam ka kammu? Kaa ko Menen saa∆īini …óam?"
  56,70,"Si Men haajuno wa…óugol …óam ndiyam …óuu…óu…óam lam…óam, hara …óam nafataa yarugol wanaa yarnirgol, ko pellet, Men wa…óayno …óum. Ko ha…ói on yettugol Allah e ko O jippiniri yurmeende Makko nden kon, ndiyam wel…óam?"
  56,71,"On yi'ii yiite nge hu…ď…ďirton haajuuji mon …óin?"
  56,72,"E ko onon tagi le…ó…óe hu…ď…ďirtee…óe ngen yiite? Kaa ko Menen tagiri …óe yurmegol on?"
  56,73,"Men wa…óir ngee yiite ko waajitoron Yiite laakara ngen, e nafitor nge setotoo…ďe mon."
  56,74,"Subbunhinor an Nulaa…óo, Joomi maa, Mawnu…óo e ko O hanndaa e mun."
  56,75,"Allah woondirii nokkuuli koode …óen."
  56,76,"Ko pellet, woondirgol mutir…óe …óee koode, ko maw…óum, si …óon anndunoo. Tawde maandeeji e tasakuyeeji no ton ko lannataa."
  56,77,"Ndee Alqur'aanaare wonaande janngeede e mon, ko Alqur'aanaare teddunde. Tawde hinde …óuu…ói nafooje maw…óe."
  56,78,"Wonnde e deftere reenaande e gite yim…ďe, nden woni Alluwal reenaangal ngal."
  56,79,"Meemataa nden, si wanaa Malaa'ika'en la…ď…ďinaa e bakkatuuji e ayiibe."
  56,80,"Ko jippiniraande ka Jey…óo tageefo ngon, e dow Annabiijo Muhammadu jom kisiyee."
  56,81,"E ko ndee yewtere woni ko fennoton, onon …ďee sirkoo…ďe fennoobe?"
  56,82,"Hi…óon wa…óira yettirgol mon Allah ngol e ko O arsikiri on neema, fennugol on …óum? Wonon e dammbirgol to…ďo ngon battinorgol hoodere (naw`u) nden? Wi'on: Men to…ďinorii hoodere naw'u kaariiree e kaariire?"
  56,83,"Ko ha…óata si ruuhu on yottike ka looko∆īere,"
  56,84,"Hara onon hi…óon ndaara ngir…ďoowo on fewndo yeeso mon on tuma."
  56,85,"Hara non ko Menen e ganndal e kattal Amen, wonndude e Malaa'ka'en Amen, …ďuri on …ďadaade maayoowo mon on, ko woni tun, on yi'ataa …ďen Malaa'ikaa…ďe."
  56,86,"Ko ha…óata on, si tawiino hara ko no aa∆īori…óon non, wonnde on immintintaake fii warjeede golle mon,"
  56,87,"Rutton kin wonkii wonuki yaltude e maayoowo mon on, si tawii ko on goongu…ďe? On hattanaa …óum."
  56,88,"Si tawii on maay…óo ko jeyaa…óo e adondirtenoo…ďe e mo∆ī∆īu…ói."
  56,89,"Haray ko fowtere nde jokkondirtaa e ronkere alah caggal mum, e arsike laa…ďu…óo, e yurmeende, e Aljanna mo o neeminotoo e mun kala ko wonkii makko faaletee, woni ko woodani mo."
  56,90,"Si tawii maay…óo on ko jeyaa…óo e yim…ďe √Īaamo …ďen, haray wata fii makko sunin; tawde ko kisal e hoolaare woodani …ďen."
  56,91,"56:90"
  56,92,"Si tawii non maay…óo on ko jeyanoo…óo e fennunoo…ďe ko Nulaa…óo on mo jam e kisiyee woni e mun on, majjunoo…ďe laawol focciingol ngol."
  56,93,"Haray jipporde makko nde o ja…ď…ďetee e mun nden, ko ndiyam fatay…óam."
  56,94,"E sumoyeede Yiite Jahiimi ngen."
  56,95,"Pellet, ko Men fillani maa kon an Nulaa…óo, ko goonga yananaa…óo, mo sikke alaa e mu'un."
  56,96,"Senin innde Joomi maa Maw…óo On, mawninaa Mo e kala ustaare!"
